Exercise 3:

Copy the code you ran for Exercise 2. This time, customize the plot by adding labs() to label the x and y axes accordingly to also include the relevant units (e.g., hrs) and include a plot title. See Making Professional Images for example.

# place your code below

  geom_point() +
  labs(x = "Sleep total (hrs)", y =  "Sleep REM (hrs)",
